PAPILLOMAVIRUS, MANATEES - USA (FLORIDA): REQUEST FOR INFO
**********************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>

Date: Mon, 15 Mar 1999 13:42:53 -0500
From: Dorothy Preslar <dpreslar@fas.org>
Source: St Petersburg Times, Florida, USA, Mon 15 Mar 1999
See Also
